<span class="comment"><font color=#000000>"Well all these incubators ended up flaming out. Why do I feel that the history will repeat itself!"<p>I don't think they will <i>all</i> flame out.  We don't seem to be.  The model is different this time.  The old model was practically an adverse selection filter.  That's why we've always resisted being called an "incubator." Though frankly we may as well give in to that, because few people now remember the previous generation of them.</font></span><p><font size=1><font color=#f6f6ef>-----</font></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table border=0><tr><td><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/s.gif" height=1 width=40></td><td valign=top><center><a id=up_3429582 href="vote?for=3429582&dir=up&whence=%2f%78%3f%66%6e%69%64%3d%35%49%48%6d%64%6d%72%58%63%74"><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/grayarrow.gif" border=0 vspace=3 hspace=2></a><span id=down_3429582></span></center></td><td class="default"><div style="margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:-10px; "><span class="comhead"><a href="user?id=davemc500hats">davemc500hats</a> 29 days ago  | <a href="item?id=3429582">link</a></span></div><br>
